389
00:28:21,929 --> 00:28:24,600
Was it yesterday? I saw a dog that looked like Cocoa.

390
00:28:25,800 --> 00:28:27,139
Jun Seo, wait up!

391
00:28:31,879 --> 00:28:32,879
