392
00:28:39,449 --> 00:28:40,449
This is nice.

393
00:29:09,419 --> 00:29:10,949
- Wake up. - What? Why?

394
00:29:11,480 --> 00:29:12,480
Are we going someplace else?

395
00:29:12,481 --> 00:29:15,250
