439
00:32:13,369 --> 00:32:14,469
You're okay.

440
00:32:15,429 --> 00:32:17,070
- Hey, look at them! - No!

441
00:32:18,070 --> 00:32:19,300
You're okay.

442
00:32:22,340 --> 00:32:23,839
- Ms. Han, it's okay. - Look!

443
00:32:23,840 --> 00:32:25,408
